                            <comment id="14465928" author="brownj" created="Sun, 14 Dec 2008 17:06:00 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;The change to throw UnsupportedOperationException instead of NullPointerException has been committed to all 3 branches (1.5, 1.6 and 1.7)&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14478359" author="paulk" created="Sun, 14 Dec 2008 21:13:34 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;We should make:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;ProxyGenerator.instantiateDelegateFromInterface(Map, &lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;Class&lt;/span&gt;)
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;follow the same behavior.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
